scene.message:
Yukino: What? Someone's down.{nl}
T-Tadashi and Tamaki?!{nl}
And Ms. Natsumi too!{waitkey}{clearbox}Why are they here...{nl}
weren't they at the school...?{nl}
D-{wait_fr:30}don't tell me!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So at last there are{nl}
victims among the ordinary{nl}
students too...{waitkey}{clearbox}A pity, but we've no time{nl}
to fuss over them.{nl}
We could be next.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Tadashi...{nl}
Tamaki...{nl}
Ms. Natsumi...{waitkey}What a cruel thing to do!{waitkey}{clearbox}Damn you, Snow Queen!{nl}
All three of you...{wait_fr:30}I'll{wait_fr:30}{nl}
avenge you, I swear it!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Zzz zzz zzz...{nl}
...hrgg{wait_fr:30}...lo...ve{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
...Tamaki-chuaaan!...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: "T...Tamaki-chuan"...{nl}
?!{nl}
Sleep-talking? Are they just{nl}
asleep, these guys?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly... worrying over{nl}
them was a waste.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wait, Mayuzumi.{nl}
Asleep or not, it's strange{nl}
that they're here when they{waitkey}{clearbox}should be at the school.{nl}
It may be the Snow Queen's{nl}
trap. Best stay cautious.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: The Tower of Hypnos...{nl}
What Hypnos symbolizes{nl}
is sleep............!{waitkey}{clearbox}Be careful, everyone!{nl}
The three may have been put{nl}
to sleep by the Snow Queen!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Zzz, zzz zzz{nl}
...mumble{wait_fr:30}...love{wait_fr:30}...you{nl}
mmm...Ta...{wait_fr:30}...da{wait_fr:30}...mumble{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: But, but~{nl}
for being put to sleep by{nl}
the Snow Queen, they're all{waitkey}{clearbox}sleeping with such{nl}
happy faces!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Zzz{wait_fr:30}...zpii{nl}
...heehee...{wait_fr:30}no...{nl}
...eat...{wait_fr:30}...properly...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
Whatever they're dreaming,{nl}
it makes me wanna pinch{waitkey}their noses.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Asleep or not, we{nl}
can't just leave the three{nl}
in a place full of monsters{waitkey}{clearbox}like this.{nl}
Let's wake them before{nl}
we go on.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Honestly,{nl}
Ms. Natsumi's{nl}
a handful too.{waitkey}{clearbox}This is no different from{nl}
her being asleep...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey,{nl}
Tadashi's always{nl}
yelling and being{waitkey}{clearbox}so noisy, but asleep{nl}
like this, he's actually{nl}
kinda pretty cute.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ahh, I'm tired.{nl}
Ayase's getting kinda{nl}
sleepy too.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: If their lives aren't{nl}
in danger, leaving them{nl}
should be no issue.{waitkey}{clearbox}We're short on time.{nl}
"Time is money."{nl}
Let's press on.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...?!{nl}
No, no. Let my guard down{nl}
even a little and I'll{waitkey}{clearbox}fall asleep.{nl}
I'd like to get out of a{nl}
place like this quickly.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What the, what the,{nl}
making us worry when they're{nl}
just asleep.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, I figured as much{nl}
from the start, y'know.{nl}
No, seriously.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: ...{wait_fr:30}......{wait_fr:30}.........{nl}
............{wait_fr:30}............{wait_fr:30}......{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}hrgg?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Wh-what?! I-I wasn't{nl}
asleep or anything!{nl}
I-I was planning strategy!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: If the reason the three{nl}
are asleep is connected{nl}
to Hypnos,{waitkey}{clearbox}then standing here like{nl}
this, I don't think they{nl}
will ever wake.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Hold firmly to your{nl}
sense of self and don't{nl}
fall asleep.{waitkey}{clearbox}That is the "key" to clearing{nl}
this "Tower of Hypnos."{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Zzz zzz zzz{nl}
hrgg...{wait_fr:30}guh...{wait_fr:30}guu...{nl}
won't... let{wait_fr:30} go...{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Zzz zzz zzz...{nl}
zzz zzz...{nl}
won't...{wait_fr:30} ever...{wait_fr:30} part...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Zzz... zzz...{nl}
zzz... zpi zpi... zpii{nl}
...don't{wait_fr:30}...run{wait_fr:30}...eat{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: ...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...!{nl}
Ow! Owowowow, my head...{nl}
hurts... I've got low blood{waitkey}{clearbox}pressure. Let me sleep{nl}
a bit more!{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}Anyway, be careful...{nl}
owww...{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Tamaki, a transfer student{nl}
in the fencing club. Fights{nl}
with Tadashi every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Tadashi, a lazy member of{nl}
the fencing club. Fights with{nl}
Tamaki every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}
